      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously preserved to the highest standard. The paint finish is flawless with a deep luster, and the interior remains in pristine, like-new condition with no signs of use. Mechanically, it performs exactly as it did the day it left the factory, offering a smooth, powerful, and whisper-quiet driving experience. This is a rare opportunity to own a perfectly maintained example that needs absolutely nothing.",
